{"type":"message","id":"50d84f52","parentId":"86f834df","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:38:19.000Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 可以，我来装。  \n先确认一下你的目标是哪一种：\n\n1. **装到 OpenClaw 里作为可用 MCP**\n2. **只是拉代码到当前工作区**\n3. **本机全局安装并帮你跑起来**\n\n如果你愿意，我也可以直接按 **OpenClaw 集成 MCP** 这个默认目标来做。  \n你回我一句：**“按 OpenClaw 装”**，我就直接开始。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0571cd91107f1b1a0169de190cbe9c8196a27a0059b7c6124f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":24963,"output":109,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25072,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776163081559,"responseId":"resp_0571cd91107f1b1a0169de190b84a8819681e9f52138db2257"}}
