{"type":"message","id":"d4197372","parentId":"d991247d","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:48:14.585Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 已按 OpenClaw 方式装好了。\n\n【结果】\n- 已克隆仓库到：\n  `/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/external/instagram-mcp`\n- 已创建虚拟环境并安装依赖\n- 已注册到 OpenClaw MCP 配置中，名字是：\n  **`instagram-mcp`**\n\n【当前注册配置】\n- command:\n  `/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/external/instagram-mcp/.venv/bin/python`\n- args:\n  `-m instagram_mcp.server`\n\n【补充说明】\n这个 MCP 本身要正常抓 Instagram，**需要代理**。项目说明里要求先配置代理，例如：\n- `http://127.0.0.1:7890`\n\n另外它默认是一个 **SSE 服务**，项目说明里默认地址是：\n- `http://127.0.0.1:8000/sse`\n\n【下一步你可以怎么用】\n如果你后面要把它接给某个支持 MCP 的运行时/客户端，用注册名 `instagram-mcp` 就行。\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步可以继续帮你做两件事之一：\n\n1. **帮你把代理也配好**\n2. **帮你实际启动并自测这个 MCP**\n\n如果要继续，你直接回我一句：\n- **“继续，配置代理”**\n或\n- **“继续，启动测试”**\n\n顺带说一句：工作区本身不是 git 仓库，所以这次没有可提交的仓库可 commit。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b21e23afab3bd860169de1b59bbb481938098b75aede633b4\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":38447,"output":344,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38791,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776163668440,"responseId":"resp_0b21e23afab3bd860169de1b577344819396af107f8ceff784"}}
