{"type":"message","id":"89c25e2f","parentId":"8a4ca419","timestamp":"2026-04-14T12:06:37.711Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 拉起来了。\n\n【当前状态】\n- 已成功启动\n- 地址：\n  **http://127.0.0.1:8011/sse**\n- 健康检查通过：\n  `http://127.0.0.1:8011/health`\n\n【为什么不是 8000】\n- 原项目默认用 `127.0.0.1:8000`\n- 但你机器的 8000 已经被别的服务占用\n- 我已经把它改到 **8011**\n\n【我已做的事】\n- 写入配置文件：\n  `~/.instagram-mcp/config.json`\n- 当前内容里已包含：\n  - host: `127.0.0.1`\n  - port: `8011`\n\n【下一步限制】\n服务虽然已经起来了，但**真正抓 Instagram 前还需要代理配置**，否则大概率拿不到数据。\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以继续帮你：\n1. **配置代理**\n2. **做一次真实接口测试**（比如查某个 Instagram 用户）\n\n你直接回：\n- **配置代理**\n或\n- **测试一个账号：用户名xxx**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0dd24f4d238bb8ff0169de2dbbbb808193bdf1077686dffe84\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":833,"output":253,"cacheRead":40832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41918,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776168377309,"responseId":"resp_0dd24f4d238bb8ff0169de2dbad2988193aa7a6f099b392282"}}
