{"type":"message","id":"0c7d62f2","parentId":"3b4e7942","timestamp":"2026-04-14T12:29:15.127Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 装好了。\n\n【已完成】\n- 已克隆到：\n  `/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/.openclaw/skills/java-audit-skills`\n\n【结构判断】\n这个仓库和刚才那个 PHP 的很像，**不是单入口 skill**，而是一个 **Java 审计子技能集合**。  \n根目录没有总 `SKILL.md`，实际可用的子技能在：\n\n`/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/.openclaw/skills/java-audit-skills/skills/`\n\n目前看到这些子技能：\n- `java-audit-pipeline`\n- `java-auth-audit`\n- `java-file-read-audit`\n- `java-file-upload-audit`\n- `java-route-mapper`\n- `java-route-tracer`\n- `java-sql-audit`\n- `java-vuln-scanner`\n- `java-xxe-audit`\n\n【这意味着什么】\n以后你给我 Java / Spring / Web 项目源码时，我可以按方向直接调用对应子技能来做，例如：\n- 路由梳理\n- 鉴权审计\n- SQL 注入审计\n- 文件读/上传问题\n- XXE\n- 漏洞入口扫描\n\n【当前状态】\n- 已安装完成\n- 不需要额外启动端口\n- 属于“本地技能包”，不是 MCP 服务\n\n【可选优化】\n如果你愿意，我也可以像刚才说的那样，帮你给这类“多子技能仓库”补一个**总入口 SKILL.md**，这样以后更方便统一触发。\n\n你接下来可以直接说：\n- `补入口`\n- `开始审 java 项目：<路径>`\n- `用这个技能看 sql 注入`\n- `先帮我验证这些 skill 是否能被识别`","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_01efaed22dd842dd0169de33003274819689264e82e1fb08d6\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":53087,"output":411,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53498,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776169724209,"responseId":"resp_01efaed22dd842dd0169de32fea28081969af7c4db47030806"}}
